    "long_instructions": "## Urban Planning\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to help plan out new features for the city.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Look at the images already uploaded to this level and decide if you'd like to use those or images of a city more relevant to you.\r\n2. Brainstorm new features you'd like to add to the city. Here are some common ones:\r\n\t- Park\r\n    - Bike lanes\r\n    - School\r\n    - Hospital\r\n    - (You can use AI chat to help you brainstorm more ideas if you'd like)\r\n3. Add the images you want to include in your input to your prompt.\r\n2. **Copy and paste** the following prompt:\r\n\r\n>Help me brainstorm ideas of where to put [insert item here] in this city.\r\n3. Press **Send**.\r\n4. Change and add to your prompt to see if you can get AI Chat to provide you more useful responses.\r\n",
